    "当前 Codex CLI 不支持恢复归档任务，请升级 Codex CLI 后重试。" : { "localizations" : { "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "This Codex CLI version cannot restore archived tasks. Upgrade it and try again." } } } },
