    "启用自动恢复" : { "localizations" : { "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Enable auto recovery" } } } },
    "检测到已启用的终止异常时，通过 Codex App 输入框发送对应提示词。" : { "localizations" : { "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "When an enabled terminal incident is detected, send its prompt through the Codex App input field." } } } },
    "未授权时不会发送，也不会使用外部 CLI；已启用规则的新异常会记录为未发送。" : { "localizations" : { "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Without access, no message is sent and no external CLI is used; new incidents for enabled rules are logged as not sent." } } } },
    "异常规则" : { "localizations" : { "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Incident rules" } } } },
    "仅终止型异常会触发；Codex 正在自动重试时不会发送。" : { "localizations" : { "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Only terminal incidents trigger recovery; nothing is sent while Codex is retrying." } } } },
    "开发者诊断" : { "localizations" : { "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Developer diagnostics" } } } },
